OL,5, Much has been written about the ways in
OL,6, which the late Silvio Berlusconi's     
OL,7, populist politics reshaped Italian     
OL,8, public life, but the ex-prime minister 
OL,9, was even better known for his lurid and
OL,10, colourful personal life.               
OL,12,FDuring his lifetime, he had a string of
OL,13,Fspouses and partners. His second wife, 
OL,14,FVeronica Lario, divorced him in 2010   
OL,15,Fafter accusing him of lying about his  
OL,16,Frelationship with a teenager.          
OL,18,FBut chief among the sex scandals that  
OL,19,Fsurrounded him was the saga of the     
OL,20,Fnotorious "bunga bunga" parties held at
OL,21,Fhis Arcore villa near Milan.           
